quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,33,"And the evil ˹consequences˺ of their deeds will unfold before them, and they will be overwhelmed by what they used to ridicule"
  45,34,"It will be said, “This Day We will neglect you as you neglected the meeting of this Day of yours! Your home will be the Fire, and you will have no helpers"
  45,35,"This is because you made a mockery of God’s revelations, and were deluded by ˹your˺ worldly life.” So ˹from˺ that Day ˹on˺ they will not be taken out of the Fire, nor will they be allowed to appease ˹their Lord˺"
  45,36,"So all praise is for God—Lord of the heavens and Lord of the earth, Lord of all worlds"
  45,37,"To Him belongs ˹all˺ Majesty in the heavens and the earth. And He is the Almighty, All-Wise"
  46,1,Ḥâ-Mĩm
  46,2,"The revelation of this Book is from God—the Almighty, All-Wise"
  46,3,We only created the heavens and the earth and everything in between for a purpose and an appointed term. Yet the disbelievers are turning away from what they have been warned about
  46,4,"Ask ˹them, O Prophet˺, “Have you considered whatever ˹idols˺ you invoke besides God? Show me what they have created on earth! Or do they have a share in ˹the creation of˺ the heavens? Bring me a scripture ˹revealed˺ before this ˹Quran˺ or a shred of knowledge, if what you say is true.”"
  46,5,"And who could be more astray than those who call upon others besides God—˹others˺ that cannot respond to them until the Day of Judgment, and are ˹even˺ unaware of their calls"